metadata.name: BoroMannequin-002
metadata.description:
Borosilicate glass Art + Dressed Mannequin Art by 3DCG

Borosilicate glass has beautiful gradations and shapes.
I believe those represents human spirits and feelings.
But physically creating huge borosilicate glass arts are
too hard.
That's why I mixed both Boro + Humanshaped Art.

3000x4245pixel
300dpi
